    "data": [
        {
            "title": "阿里巴巴早前以7億美元售Trendyol GO的85%股權 上半財年從螞蟻收股息4.63億美元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">阿里巴巴(09988)在剛刊發的2026年度中期報告中披露，於5月訂立協議出售Trendyol GO的85%權益，對價7億美元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"Trendyol GO 官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/Trendyol-Web.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"Trendyol GO 官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/12/Trendyol-Web.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">Trendyol GO 官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">根據中期報告，上述交易對價7億美元約相等於50億元人民幣，但出售事項產生收益則約達60億元人民幣，交易已於2026年財年的上半年(即截至今年9月底止半年)內完成。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">Trendyol GO是Trendyol旗下全資子公司，在土耳其經營本地生活服務業務。在出售完成後，阿里巴巴尚持Trendyol GO餘巰5%股權。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">中期報告又顯示，在截至9月底時，阿里巴巴於螞蟻集團在全面攤薄基礎上的股權為33%。在截至9月底止半年，阿里巴巴從螞蟻集團收到股息，合共4.63億美元，相等於32.93億元人民幣。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15479155-%e9%98%bf%e9%87%8c%e5%b7%b4%e5%b7%b4%e6%97%a9%e5%89%8d%e4%bb%a57%e5%84%84%e7%be%8e%e5%85%83%e5%94%aetrendyol-go%e7%9a%8485%e8%82%a1%e6%ac%8a-%e4%b8%8a%e5%8d%8a%e8%b2%a1%e5%b9%b4%e5%be%9e%e8%9e%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240619_FI_source-web_09988-2.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 09:55:32",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "滬指開市升1點 深成指升2點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地股市初段變動不大，上證綜指以3879點開市，升1點或0.04%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指開市報12957點，亦升2點或0.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數升2點或0.06%，開報4533點；創業板指數開市報3037點，升不足1點或0.01%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15479133-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%e5%8d%871%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%88%90%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%872%e9%bb%9e",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/05/20150819_FI_AShare_4-2_source-ap_.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 09:30:34",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "港股開市︱初段略彈 恒指回升43點報25804點 澳達復牌炒高1.15倍",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股開市初段略作反彈，恒生指數開市報25804點，升43點或0.17%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒生科技指數開報5546點，升11點或0.21%；國企指數以9051點開市，升23點或0.26%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">重磅股互有升跌，阿里巴巴(09988)今早在港開報153.1元，跌0.33%；騰訊(00700)開報610元，跌0.16%；美團(03690)開報96.8元，升0.94%；京東(09618)開報116.2元，升0.61%；小米(01810)開報40.34元，升0.3%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">兩大藍籌國際金融股當中，滙控(00005)開報111.1元，逆市微跌0.09%；友邦(01299)開報79.55元，暫時無升跌。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230704-174447_source-web_美團1_source-web_.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：美團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2023/07/bplib_20230704-174447_source-web_美團1_source-web_.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：美團官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">均勝電子(00699)獲調入港股通，該股今早開報18元，升1.12%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">萬物雲(02602)擬斥最多5億元人民幣回購H股，該股今早開報20.16元，升1.66%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">澳達控股(09929)獲深圳上市公司姚記科技(002605.SZ)董事長姚朔斌收購控股權，並以同價每股0.11元提全面收購，作價較停牌前收市價有溢價6.36%；該股今早復牌應聲炒上，以0.221元開市，飆1.15%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15479126-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e7%95%a5%e5%bd%88-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%8743%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b125804%e9%bb%9e-%e6%be%b3%e9%81%94%e5%be%a9%e7%89%8c%e7%82%92",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-12-04 09:30:36",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "即月期指開報25859點 高水98點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指開報25859點，升118點，較上日現貨收市價25760點高水98點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月科指期貨開報5553點，升23點，高水18點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月國指期貨開報9056點，升36點，高水27點。</p>\n</div>",
